            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page5');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page5",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "It was only because I lost to you back then that I could become even stronger."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page6');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page6",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "I'm sure that you and your Pok\u00e9mon must have had to overcome a lot, too..."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page7');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page7",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "type": "expression",
                    "expression": "'To make it all the way here. Right, ' + q.player.username + '?'"
                }
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page8');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page8",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "Everyone's grown so much..."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page9');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page9",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "And now we'll finally get to see just what we all can do."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page10');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page10",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "Standing here facing you again gives me chills..."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": [
                            "q.run_command('scoreboard players set ' + q.player.username + ' BattleStart 38');",
                            "q.run_command('execute as ' + q.player.username + ' run function hoenn:triggers/stopsound');",
                          "q.dialogue.set_page('page11');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page11",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "...But I won't give up! I won't lose anymore."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.set_page('page12');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page12",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "My Pok\u00e9mon have given me the courage and strength to fight."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page13');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page13",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "I have to win for their sake!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Next...",
                        "value": "next",
                        "action": "q.dialogue.set_page('page14');"
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "page14",
            "speaker": "wally",
            "lines": [
                "So get ready... Here I come!"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": false,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "\u00a7c\u2694 Battle \u2694\u00a7r",
